<i>noun</i>: 용두사미 [용두사미] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>용두사미 [용두사미]</dt><br>
<dd>anticlimax</dd><br>
<dd>시작할 때는 거창하고 대단해 보이지만 끝으로 갈수록 점점 기세가 줄어드는 일이나 상황.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or situation in which the beginning is grandiose and impressive, yet the finish is disappointing as it loses momentum.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>